title: NEMA 17 adapter for Namiki DC Servo Motor
description: This is a plate to adapt the high quality coreless namiki DC servo motors with encoders that can be found on ebay to mount with anything that will take a  NEMA 17 footprint. These can be used to implement closed loop control for systems that used to use steppers. The shaft diameter is a bit less than the standard NEMA 17 one, (4.5 instead of 5mm) but a piece of rubber tubing around it can be used if you need it to fit an existing mount.

title: FlashForge Creator Pro extended bed levelling code
description: This is an x3g file that can be used to check how level and flat your printing platform really is. It is meant for the FlashForge Creator Pro, but will probably work for similar printers as well.

title: Mojo SD Card Adapter
description: This is a Chord Mojo SD Card Adapter, reads SDXC cards, works with Android (native Android support or USB Audio Player Pro), should work with Windows/MAC OS, technically it is only a usb hub and a card reader. Expand your smartphone/tablet memory with a cheap SD Card.

title: Quick Start Shells for Gogoro EV key fob.
description:
These Gogoro Key fob shell give you a quick start via press almost anywhere on the shell instead of seeking the specific spot to do so.
There are 3 types I have made: 1. Necklace Biscuit, 2. Necklace Clam(hinged) 3. Weist Band for a watch belt set in 24mm width.
The screw cover to fix the key fob cover is a common for all types.
The key fob cover are common parts for type 1 and 3.

title: Gardinenstangenclip Ersatzteil
description:
Ersatz für einen Gardinenstangenclip zur Befestigung von 10mm Stangen. Das Loch auf der Unterseite des Holzknauf ist 17.2mm.
Auf einer Seite des Fensters war der Clip für die Gardinenstangenbefestigung zerbrochen deshalb habe ich diesen mit FreeCad neu entworfen und ausgedruckt. Die CAD-Datei im FreeCad-Format habe ich beigefügt.
Zum Drucken habe ich normales PLA verwendet und 100% Füllung eingestellt. Der neue selbstgemachte Clip hält die Gardinenstange etwas strammer als das Originalteil
